description: Papa D’z Pizza Fresca is a world class company providing the best pizza’s using only the finest ingredients made fresh at any location. We believe in going the extra mile and not only serving the best pizza but preparing, baking and serving it at your special event making all of the difference. Papa D’z understands that preparing and hosting a special event is hard enough without having to worry about cooking, cleaning up the mess and no one wants to order “delivery”! Frozen pizza? Forget about it! We prepare, bake, and serve our pizza’s on the spot, fresh and hot. Papa D’z takes care of it all. We show up, set up, and clean up so we can leave you and your guests with a smile every time.
name: Papa D'z Pizza
